Name: That Last Girl
About the game: First person, Indie, single level, horror survival game. Use light and sound-based strategies to evade the ghost in an atmospheric factory. Intelligent monster, no set patrols, no endless random movement. She will hunt you down. Use light, sound and the factory layout itself to your advantage. Achieve all the Objectives to unlock the extended ending.
